data.description: Beautiful, updated home in the highly desirable neighborhood of Emerald Shores ~ just 1.5 miles to the back gate of NAS Pensacola, and minutes to the beaches of Perdido Key! * The Great Room is expansive, with high ceilings and plant ledges; the Kitchen boasts an island, tons of countertop/cabinet space, and a pantry for plenty of storage * The Master Bedroom is large and enjoys double vanities and large garden tub/shower combo! * The home rests on a half-acre lot; the huge backyard has plenty of room for activities, and there is also a patio for BBQ’s, entertaining and get-togethers! * This property has SO much to offer & the location is second to none *** Please verify all features, dimensions, measurements, etc that may be important to you
